Johannesburg- Media personality and actress Pearl Thusi has agreed to go on a lunch date with Twitter influencer Mr.Smeg. This comes after Mr. Smeg as he is affectionately known on Twitter shot his shot at Peal Thusi and asked her out on a lunch date. “Hi @PearlThusi, May I take you out for lunch?”  Pearl surprisingly replied to Mr. smeg’s date request and they agreed on a day and venue of their lunch date.   “Why don’t we support black & go to Daruma by @OskidoIBelieve or signature, Gemelli might be too loud if it gets packed. And if I’m not gigging then I’ll take you to@KonkaSoweto after I’ll take other suggestions too.”  Since then Mr. Smeg has been beaming with excitement for his date on Saturday and has asked anyone who wishes to dress him up to do so. “Lunch date with Pearl Thusi at Daruma on Saturday”  “My DM is open is open if you want to dress me for the lunch date with Pearl Thusi.”   For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here